data.description: Enchanting residence showcasing impeccable mid-century modern features, nestled on an expansive .38-acre, private lot. This residence exudes warmth with beautiful hardwood flooring throughout. Abundant natural light fills the living room, thanks to the numerous windows that surround the space. The cozy gas fireplace adds a touch of comfort, while the built-in shelving around the entryway door gives the home an elegant feel. The adjacent dining area offers easy transition to the outdoors with sliders that open up to the expansive backyard. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, lots of cabinetry for all your storage needs, and a convenient eat-at bar for quick meals and morning coffee. The spacious primary bedroom has double closets and a private bath, providing privacy at the end of the day. Two additional good-sized bedrooms and a full bath offer comfort for family and guests. The large, fenced backyard has a covered patio, a greenhouse and RV parking, making this outdoor space perfect for enjoying the beautiful Pacific Northwest weather. Separate, finished shop for your hobbies or potential ADU. Conveniently located, this home provides easy access to restaurants, shopping, parks, and I-205.
